Leamington (Ontario).title: Leamington (Ontario)
Leamington (Ontario).byline: Leamington is a municipality of about 30,000 people (2021) in Essex County, Ontario, and the southern-most city in Canada.

Leamington Spa.title: Leamington Spa
Leamington Spa.byline: Royal Leamington Spa (or Leamington Spa or simply Leamington) is a spa town of 51,000 people (2021) in the West Midlands region of England, close to the cities of Coventry and Birmingham.
